# The Constitution Of The United States Of America

**
[ 58f70c9ebc843cbf9384db87a92633e238e013ee Gouverneur Morris Draft ]
We the People
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]
**
[ 58f70c9ebc843cbf9384db87a92633e238e013ee Gouverneur Morris Draft ]
 of the
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]
 United
[ 58f70c9ebc843cbf9384db87a92633e238e013ee Gouverneur Morris Draft ]
 States,
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]
 in Order to form a more perfect Union
[ 58f70c9ebc843cbf9384db87a92633e238e013ee Gouverneur Morris Draft ]
,
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]

establish Justice, insure domestic Tranquility, provide for the common defence
[ 58f70c9ebc843cbf9384db87a92633e238e013ee Gouverneur Morris Draft ]
,
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]

promote the general Welfare
[ 58f70c9ebc843cbf9384db87a92633e238e013ee Gouverneur Morris Draft ]
, and
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]
 secure the Blessings of Liberty to ourselves
and our Posterity
[ 58f70c9ebc843cbf9384db87a92633e238e013ee Gouverneur Morris Draft ]
, do ordain and establish
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]
 this
[ 58f70c9ebc843cbf9384db87a92633e238e013ee Gouverneur Morris Draft ]
 Constitution for the United
States of America.

## Article. I.
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]


**Section. 1.**  All
[ 58f70c9ebc843cbf9384db87a92633e238e013ee Gouverneur Morris Draft ]
 legislative Powers
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]
 herein granted
[ 58f70c9ebc843cbf9384db87a92633e238e013ee Gouverneur Morris Draft ]
 shall be vested in a
Congress
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]
 of the United States
[ 58f70c9ebc843cbf9384db87a92633e238e013ee Gouverneur Morris Draft ]
,
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]
 which shall
[ 58f70c9ebc843cbf9384db87a92633e238e013ee Gouverneur Morris Draft ]
 consist of a Senate
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]
 and House
[ 58f70c9ebc843cbf9384db87a92633e238e013ee Gouverneur Morris Draft ]
 of
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]

Representatives.
[ 7f340829cfc2ea844de1adfa4d9618d2adb6f932 James Madison Bill of Rights ]
 Congress shall make no law respecting an establishment of
religion, or prohibiting the free exercise thereof; or abridging the freedom of
speech, or of the press; or the right of the people peaceably to assemble, and
to petition the government for a redress of grievances.
[ d76baa1a4d69eedf2658225064b40f94a5deed26 John Bingham Amendment XIV ]


No person shall be a Senator or Representative in Congress, or elector of President and Vice President, or hold any office, civil or military, under the United States, or under any State, who, having previously taken an oath, as a member of Congress, or as an officer of the United States, or as a member of any State legislature, or as an executive or judicial officer of any State, to support the Constitution of the United States, shall have engaged in insurrection or rebellion against the same, or given aid or comfort to the enemies thereof. But Congress may, by a vote of two-thirds of each House, remove such disability.
[ 0cdbb927a04363d0bfd61bcfa35954e873f6dd91 Congress Amendment XX ]


The terms of Senators and Representatives shall end at noon
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]
 on the
[ 0cdbb927a04363d0bfd61bcfa35954e873f6dd91 Congress Amendment XX ]
 3d day of
January, of the years
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]
 in
[ 0cdbb927a04363d0bfd61bcfa35954e873f6dd91 Congress Amendment XX ]
 which such terms end; and the terms of their
successors shall then begin.
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]


**Section. 2.**  The House of Representatives
[ 58f70c9ebc843cbf9384db87a92633e238e013ee Gouverneur Morris Draft ]
 shall
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]
 be composed of
[ 58f70c9ebc843cbf9384db87a92633e238e013ee Gouverneur Morris Draft ]
 Members
chosen every second Year by the People of the several States
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]
, and the Electors
in each State shall have the Qualifications requisite for Electors of the most
numerous Branch of the State Legislature.

No Person shall be a Representative who shall not have attained to the Age of
twenty five Years, and been seven Years a Citizen of the United States, and who
shall not, when elected, be an Inhabitant of that State in which he shall be
chosen.

Representatives shall be apportioned among the several States according to
their respective numbers,
[ d76baa1a4d69eedf2658225064b40f94a5deed26 John Bingham Amendment XIV ]
 counting
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]
 the whole number
[ 58f70c9ebc843cbf9384db87a92633e238e013ee Gouverneur Morris Draft ]
 of
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]
 persons
[ d76baa1a4d69eedf2658225064b40f94a5deed26 John Bingham Amendment XIV ]
 in each State
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]
,
excluding Indians not taxed
[ d76baa1a4d69eedf2658225064b40f94a5deed26 John Bingham Amendment XIV ]
. But when the right to vote at any election for the
choice
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]
 of
[ d76baa1a4d69eedf2658225064b40f94a5deed26 John Bingham Amendment XIV ]
 electors for President and Vice President of the United States,
Representatives in Congress, the Executive and Judicial officers of a State, or
the members of the Legislature thereof, is denied to any of the male
inhabitants of such State, being twenty-one years of age, and citizens of the
United States, or in any way abridged, except for participation in rebellion,
or
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]
 other
[ d76baa1a4d69eedf2658225064b40f94a5deed26 John Bingham Amendment XIV ]
 crime, the basis of representation therein shall be reduced in the
proportion which the number of such male citizens shall bear to the whole
number of male citizens twenty-one years of age in such State
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]
. The actual
Enumeration shall be made within three Years after the first Meeting of the
Congress of the United States
[ 58f70c9ebc843cbf9384db87a92633e238e013ee Gouverneur Morris Draft ]
,
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]
 and within every subsequent Term of ten Years
[ 58f70c9ebc843cbf9384db87a92633e238e013ee Gouverneur Morris Draft ]
,
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]

in such Manner
[ 58f70c9ebc843cbf9384db87a92633e238e013ee Gouverneur Morris Draft ]
 as
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]
 they shall by Law direct. The Number of Representatives shall
not exceed one for
[ 58f70c9ebc843cbf9384db87a92633e238e013ee Gouverneur Morris Draft ]
 every
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]
 thirty Thousand, but each State
[ 58f70c9ebc843cbf9384db87a92633e238e013ee Gouverneur Morris Draft ]
 shall
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]
 have
[ 58f70c9ebc843cbf9384db87a92633e238e013ee Gouverneur Morris Draft ]
