[ dcb04e72a52f251cba092eb88b905d6d0b9a8d7b House of Representatives Amendment XVII ]
 people
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]
 thereof, for six years; and
[ 58f70c9ebc843cbf9384db87a92633e238e013ee Gouverneur Morris Draft ]

each
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]
 Senator
[ 58f70c9ebc843cbf9384db87a92633e238e013ee Gouverneur Morris Draft ]
 shall have one vote.
[ dcb04e72a52f251cba092eb88b905d6d0b9a8d7b House of Representatives Amendment XVII ]
 The electors in each State shall have the
qualifications requisite for electors of the most numerous branch of the State
legislatures.
[ 58f70c9ebc843cbf9384db87a92633e238e013ee Gouverneur Morris Draft ]


Immediately after
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]
 they shall be assembled in Consequence of
[ 58f70c9ebc843cbf9384db87a92633e238e013ee Gouverneur Morris Draft ]
 the first Election
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]
,
[ 58f70c9ebc843cbf9384db87a92633e238e013ee Gouverneur Morris Draft ]

they shall be divided
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]
 as equally as may be
[ 58f70c9ebc843cbf9384db87a92633e238e013ee Gouverneur Morris Draft ]
 into three Classes. The Seats of the
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]

Senators
[ 58f70c9ebc843cbf9384db87a92633e238e013ee Gouverneur Morris Draft ]
