[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]
**
[ 58f70c9ebc843cbf9384db87a92633e238e013ee Gouverneur Morris Draft ]
 The executive Power shall be vested in a President of the
United States of America. He shall hold his Office during the Term of
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]
 four
[ 58f70c9ebc843cbf9384db87a92633e238e013ee Gouverneur Morris Draft ]

Years
[ 0cdbb927a04363d0bfd61bcfa35954e873f6dd91 Congress Amendment XX ]
 ending at noon on the 20th day of January
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]
, and, together with the Vice
President, chosen for the same Term, be elected, as follows

Each State shall appoint, in such Manner as the Legislature thereof may direct,
a Number of Electors, equal to the whole Number of Senators and Representatives
to which the State may be entitled in the Congress:
[ 58f70c9ebc843cbf9384db87a92633e238e013ee Gouverneur Morris Draft ]
 but
[ 0ab6fd623757e034e86d87df07efaa38626f765e Constitutional Convention We the People ]
 no Senator or
Representative, or Person holding an Office of Trust or Profit under the United
States, shall be appointed an Elector.
[ 90025bf2e2b2ba0f762136012e3cf1d60510e49f Congress Amendement XXV ]


**SubSection. 1.**
