## Article. VIII.
[ 7868b033b9251a802bbd302eb49c25dc0cd3e169 Senate Amendment XVII ]


**Section 1.** The
[ e04f1c0f38a21cee805e2d298ea147e3a68fcc6c Congress Amendment XXI ]
 transportation or importation into any State
[ 7868b033b9251a802bbd302eb49c25dc0cd3e169 Senate Amendment XVII ]
,
[ e04f1c0f38a21cee805e2d298ea147e3a68fcc6c Congress Amendment XXI ]
 Territory
[ 7868b033b9251a802bbd302eb49c25dc0cd3e169 Senate Amendment XVII ]
, or
[ e04f1c0f38a21cee805e2d298ea147e3a68fcc6c Congress Amendment XXI ]

possession of the United States for delivery or use therein
[ 7868b033b9251a802bbd302eb49c25dc0cd3e169 Senate Amendment XVII ]
 of intoxicating
liquors,
[ e04f1c0f38a21cee805e2d298ea147e3a68fcc6c Congress Amendment XXI ]
 in violation of
[ 7868b033b9251a802bbd302eb49c25dc0cd3e169 Senate Amendment XVII ]
 the
[ e04f1c0f38a21cee805e2d298ea147e3a68fcc6c Congress Amendment XXI ]
 laws
[ 7868b033b9251a802bbd302eb49c25dc0cd3e169 Senate Amendment XVII ]
 thereof, is hereby prohibited.